{"tid":1905792,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"英報：C.朗拿度捲入新冠病毒恐慌 確診傳染鏈指向祖記","createTime":"2020-03-01T13:19:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-01T19:21:03.000Z","uid":173952,"like":9,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"88ca94fd7a20faf6776c3032a770af98ba5d0edc","tid":1905792,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T13:19:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cgFuj2S.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcgFuj2S.jpg&h=9b02a645&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a828cde96d9bf8cbd9f9bd98d7f7628aaa20393","tid":1905792,"uid":173952,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T13:21:52.000Z","msg":"在上週日的比賽中，祖記U23隊與皮亞內塞隊進行了一場第三級別比賽，而本週爆出的消息稱，皮亞內塞隊參與該場比賽的三名球員與一名教練檢測陽性，成為新冠確診病例，這引發了祖雲達斯球會的高度警惕。<br />\n<br />\n  令人擔心的是，<span style=\"color: red;\">一些參加了那場比賽的祖記U23球員，在周中和C.朗拿度以及祖記一隊有過一次合練</span>，如今U23對手新冠確診病例的消息曝出，接下來幾週祖記球會都不會再安排這樣的合練。<br />\n<br />\n  祖記球會內部已開始對球員們進行檢測，目前沒有發現有陽性案例，祖雲達斯球會的一個線人透露：「情況被認真對待，醫療組告訴所有球員要勤洗手。」"},{"pid":"597cd228e11242853170e11687981ded5da68eb0","tid":1905792,"uid":32586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T13:23:41.000Z","msg":"阿朗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b345b906bf5739476aa3ebde78cdf212f1dbd39","tid":1905792,"uid":9542,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T13:25:18.000Z","msg":"係咪擁抱過支那人"},{"pid":"dcf995ae7b6bcde2e307d5f177964ac2245fb025","tid":1905792,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T13:27:59.000Z","msg":"潛伏期14日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60a63178d2beb41b30cde801f1514af46e1744df","tid":1905792,"uid":233327,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTi